Class LSEAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • amesmarket.LSEAgent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    uchicago.src.sim.gui.Drawable

    public class LSEAgent
extends java.lang.Object
implements uchicago.src.sim.gui.Drawable
    Load serving entity (wholesale power buyer).

    Example showing what lseData[i] contains

    LSEData 
     ID     atBus   block   LP      block   LP      block   LP      block   LP
 1      1       6       22      6       30      6       34      6       27
    block: load block for the next how many hours LP: load profile (fixed demand)
